	<texsetting wysiwyg="0"/><paper pagenumber="1" margin="20,20,20,25">A4</paper></head>
	
<body fontsize="12pt" fontface="ＭＳ Ｐ明朝">
<p>酔っ払いは１回の跳躍でぴょんと距離<mblock><munit italic="1">a</munit></mblock>だけ動くと仮定しよう。但しそれが</p>
<p>東か西かは同様に確からしいとする。</p>
<p/>
<p>さて<mblock><munit italic="1">n</munit></mblock>回(<mblock><munit italic="1">n</munit></mblock>は十分大きな整数とする)の跳躍の後、粒子は(今後簡単に粒子にする)<mblock><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit></mblock>の位置にいたとする。<mblock><munit italic="1">m</munit></mblock>は正にも</p>
<p>負にもなり得るが、<mblock><marray type="vert"><melem><munit italic="1">m</munit></melem></marray><munit entity="1">leq</munit><munit italic="1">n</munit></mblock>が成立する。</p>
<p/>
<p>右に跳んだ回数を<mblock><munit italic="1">n<mlink type="rsub"><munit>+</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>、左に跳んだ回数を<mblock><munit italic="1">n<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">minus</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>とすると、直ちに</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">n<mlink type="rsub"><munit>+</munit></mlink></munit><munit>+</munit><munit italic="1">n<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">minus</munit></mlink></munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">n<mlink type="rsub"><munit>+</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">n<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">minus</munit></mlink></munit></mblock></p>
<p>であることが導かれる。但し<mblock><munit italic="1">m</munit></mblock>にたどり着くまで右<mblock><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">n<mlink type="rsub"><munit>+</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>と左<mblock><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">n<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">minus</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>をどのように組み合わせてもいい。</p>
<p>組み合わせの数<mblock><munit italic="1">W<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>が多いほどその場所<mblock><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>にたどり着く確率が多いことは分かるだろう。そこで</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">n</munit></mblock>回の跳躍で<mblock><munit italic="1">m</munit></mblock>にたどり着く場合の数<mblock><munit italic="1">W<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>は</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">W<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>!</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n<mlink type="rsub"><munit>+</munit></mlink></munit><munit>!</munit><munit italic="1">n<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">minus</munit></mlink></munit><munit>!</munit></mlink></munit></mblock></p>
<p>である。また先程の式から</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">n<mlink type="rsub"><munit>+</munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>+</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">n<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">minus</munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mblock></p>
<p>となり、これを上の式に代入すれば、<mblock><munit italic="1">W<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>を求めることができる。しかしこれはとても</p>
<p>大きな数になるので、その対数をとって<mblock><munit entity="1">log</munit><munit italic="1">W<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>を計算しよう。</p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1">log</munit><munit italic="1">W<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">log</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>!</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>+</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit>!</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit>!</munit></mlink></munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">n</munit></mblock>が十分大きいので、<mblock><munit entity="1">log</munit><munit italic="1">z</munit><munit>!</munit><munit entity="1">simeq</munit><munit italic="1">z</munit><munit entity="1">log</munit><munit italic="1">z</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">z</munit></mblock>を代入して、</p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1">log</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>!</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>+</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit>!</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit>!</munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit entity="1">log</munit><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>+</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit entity="1">log</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>+</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit>+</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>+</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit entity="1">minus</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit entity="1">log</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit>+</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">n</munit><marray type="curly"><melem><munit entity="1">log</munit><munit>2</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit>1</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit entity="1">log</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit>1</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit>1</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit entity="1">log</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit>1</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray></melem></marray></mblock></p>
<p>となる。ここで</p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1">log</munit><munit>(</munit><munit>1</munit><munit>+</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit><munit entity="1">simeq</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsup"><munit>3</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>3</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsup"><munit>4</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>4</munit></mlink></munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit> </munit><munit> </munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit entity="1">ll</munit><munit>1</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
<p>を使って</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">n</munit><marray type="curly"><melem><munit entity="1">log</munit><munit>2</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit>1</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit entity="1">log</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit>1</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit>1</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit entity="1">log</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit>1</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray></melem></marray><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">log</munit><munit>2<mlink type="rsup"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="curly"><melem><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit>1</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit>+</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit>1</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray></melem></marray></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">log</munit><munit>2<mlink type="rsup"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit></mblock></p>
<p>従って</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">W<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>2<mlink type="rsup"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">exp</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">A</munit><munit entity="1">exp</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit italic="1">a<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">W<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">x</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">a</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>を確率とみなして、係数<mblock><munit italic="1">A</munit></mblock>を決めよう。</p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1" style="big">int<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">infty</munit></mlink><mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">infty</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">A</munit><munit entity="1">exp</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit italic="1">a<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit></mblock></p>
<p>より、</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">W<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" style="big">sqrt<mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">pi</munit><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">a</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">exp</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit italic="1">a<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray></mblock></p>
<p>となる。</p>
